DISCLAIMER
----------
Reachable aggregates and analyzes data from multiple internal and third-party
security tools and sources. The accuracy, completeness, and timeliness of its
outputs are inherently dependent on the quality, coverage, and reliability of
those sources. Reachable does not guarantee that its findings represent a
complete or definitive view of security risks or compliance posture.
Furthermore, compliance frameworks and standards—including, but not limited to,
SOC 2, ISO 27001, NIST, and CIS—are continuously evolving, and Reachable's
outputs should be interpreted as risk-informed guidance rather than a
certification, assurance, or absolute measure of compliance.
